[SHORT DESC]
The user always moves first. Will only work if the foe attacked.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Attacks with priority. This move only works if the target uses a damaging attack. This move fails if the target moves before the user (for instance, if they use a move of higher priority, or if they use a move of equal priority and are faster). This move is not powered up by the ability Iron Fist.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/extremespeed">ExtremeSpeed</a> is a Normal-type equivalent, but does not require the target to attack.</p>